" xml:id=\"sub-1488\">- Women in power.</p><p begin=\"01:19:14.77\" end=\"01:19:16.54\" xml:id=\"sub-1489\">His drive and his weakness.</p><p begin=\"01:19:16.86\" end=\"01:19:19.64\" xml:id=\"sub-1490\">He desires them, and <br/>he despises that desire.</p><p begin=\"01:19:20.39\" end=\"01:19:22.87\" xml:id=\"sub-1491\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">How can a man reconcile <br/>his need for domination</span></p><p begin=\"01:19:23.02\" end=\"01:19:24.52\" xml:id=\"sub-1492\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">with his need to remain a man?</span></p><p begin=\"01:19:26.43\" end=\"01:19:28.52\" xml:id=\"sub-1493\">- By killing the thing he desires.</p><p begin=\"01:19:28.98\" end=\"01:19:29.87\" xml:id=\"sub-1494\">- You're a fast learner.</p><p begin=\"01:19:30.32\" end=\"01:19:31.51\" xml:id=\"sub-1495\">- He didn't desire the café owner.</p><p begin=\"01:19:31.77\" end=\"01:19:33.32\" xml:id=\"sub-1496\">- Oh, he's chosen another victim,</p><p begin=\"01:19:34.07\" end=\"01:19:35.72\" xml:id=\"sub-1497\">but this victim is difficult.</p><p begin=\"01:19:36.09\" end=\"01:19:36.74\" xml:id=\"sub-1498\">Scares him.</p><p begin=\"01:19:37.72\" end=\"01:19:38.67\" xml:id=\"sub-1499\">But he needs to kill.</p><p begin=\"01:19:39.27\" end=\"01:19:40.36\" xml:id=\"sub-1500\">He must.</p><p begin=\"01:19:40.90\" end=\"01:19:45.27\" xml:id=\"sub-1501\">The café owner or a chance <br/>encounter satiate the need</p><p begin=\"01:19:46.10\" end=\"01:19:47.69\" xml:id=\"sub-1502\">but simply are marking time.</p><p begin=\"01:19:48.07\" end=\"01:19:49.14\" xml:id=\"sub-1503\">- How does that help us find 'im?</p><p begin=\"01:19:50.28\" end=\"01:19:51.99\" xml:id=\"sub-1504\">- You already know <br/>where to look for him.</p><p begin=\"01:19:53.19\" end=\"01:19:55.86\" xml:id=\"sub-1505\">A writer can't help <br/>but bare his soul.</p><p begin=\"01:19:57.03\" end=\"01:19:59.13\" xml:id=\"sub-1506\">- [Marion] The other victims were <br/>attacked first in the newspaper.</p><p begin=\"01:20:01.48\" end=\"01:20:02.53\" xml:id=\"sub-1507\">- He's coming after you.</p><p begin=\"01:20:04.27\" end=\"01:20:05.58\" xml:id=\"sub-1508\">Well, you-- you need <br/>some protection:</p><p begin=\"01:20:05.98\" end=\"01:20:07.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1509\">bodyguards, maybe a safe house.</p><p begin=\"01:20:08.26\" end=\"01:20:08.76\" xml:id=\"sub-1510\">[chuckle]</p><p begin=\"01:20:09.04\" end=\"01:20:10.71\" xml:id=\"sub-1511\">- He's obsessed with <br/>women in power.</p><p begin=\"01:20:10.83\" end=\"01:20:12.60\" xml:id=\"sub-1512\">I don't think it's me <br/>who needs protecting.</p><p begin=\"01:20:15.22\" end=\"01:20:19.91\" xml:id=\"sub-1513\">♪ [music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:20:20.15\" end=\"01:20:20.73\" xml:id=\"sub-1514\">[car door clicks closed]</p><p begin=\"01:20:22.07\" end=\"01:20:25.05\" xml:id=\"sub-1515\">[footsteps fade]</p><p begin=\"01:20:25.55\" end=\"01:20:26.05\" xml:id=\"sub-1516\">[computer beep]</p><p begin=\"01:20:36.77\" end=\"01:20:37.37\" xml:id=\"sub-1517\">[computer beep]</p><p begin=\"01:20:41.40\" end=\"01:20:43.17\" xml:id=\"sub-1518\">[car motors past]</p><p begin=\"01:20:51.14\" end=\"01:20:54.01\" xml:id=\"sub-1519\">♪ [suspenseful music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:20:54.13\" end=\"01:20:55.63\" xml:id=\"sub-1520\">[clock ticking]</p><p begin=\"01:21:00.09\" end=\"01:21:00.61\" xml:id=\"sub-1521\">[gasp]</p><p begin=\"01:21:00.75\" end=\"01:21:01.41\" xml:id=\"sub-1522\">- Can't sleep?</p><p begin=\"01:21:03.86\" end=\"01:21:04.65\" xml:id=\"sub-1523\">- How'd you get in?</p><p begin=\"01:21:05.75\" end=\"01:21:06.72\" xml:id=\"sub-1524\">- Our wonderful night together.</p><p begin=\"01:21:07.63\" end=\"01:21:08.53\" xml:id=\"sub-1525\">I found yer spare key.</p><p begin=\"01:21:11.04\" end=\"01:21:11.71\" xml:id=\"sub-1526\">- What do you want?</p><p begin=\"01:21:11.87\" end=\"01:21:12.92\" xml:id=\"sub-1527\">- I had to see you again.</p><p begin=\"01:21:13.55\" end=\"01:21:14.05\" xml:id=\"sub-1528\">[pistol clicks]</p><p begin=\"01:21:14.10\" end=\"01:21:15.30\" xml:id=\"sub-1529\">- You don't move.</p><p begin=\"01:21:15.86\" end=\"01:21:16.72\" xml:id=\"sub-1530\">- Looks like you got me.</p><p begin=\"01:21:18.12\" end=\"01:21:19.37\" xml:id=\"sub-1531\">Does it make you <br/>feel strong, Susan?</p><p begin=\"01:21:19.97\" end=\"01:21:20.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1532\">A gun in your hand?</p><p begin=\"01:21:21.52\" end=\"01:21:22.39\" xml:id=\"sub-1533\">Does it give you the edge?</p><p begin=\"01:21:22.86\" end=\"01:21:23.70\" xml:id=\"sub-1534\">- Go to the livin' room.</p><p begin=\"01:21:30.41\" end=\"01:21:31.72\" xml:id=\"sub-1535\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[radio voice] Calling DI <br/>Creegan. Come in.</span></p><p begin=\"01:21:33.40\" end=\"01:21:34.12\" xml:id=\"sub-1536\">- Go ahead, Mark.</p><p begin=\"01:21:34.89\" end=\"01:21:36.75\" xml:id=\"sub-1537\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Rivers] Yeah. We got another <br/>message from Laney.</span></p><p begin=\"01:21:38.69\" end=\"01:21:39.37\" xml:id=\"sub-1538\">- You trace it?</p><p begin=\"01:21:40.64\" end=\"01:21:41.65\" xml:id=\"sub-1539\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Rivers] It came from <br/>the &quot;Daily News.&quot;</span></p><p begin=\"01:21:43.07\" end=\"01:21:43.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1540\">- All right. I'll meet you there.</p><p begin=\"01:21:44.65\" end=\"01:21:45.55\" xml:id=\"sub-1541\">Control, this is Creegan.</p><p begin=\"01:21:46.46\" end=\"01:21:47.09\" xml:id=\"sub-1542\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[radio voice] Control.</span></p><p begin=\"01:21:47.54\" end=\"01:21:50.36\" xml:id=\"sub-1543\">- Yeah. DI Taylor's flat. I want <br/>two cars, front and back,</p><p begin=\"01:21:51.11\" end=\"01:21:52.21\" xml:id=\"sub-1544\">and don't let her <br/>know you're there.</p><p begin=\"01:21:58.27\" end=\"01:22:00.58\" xml:id=\"sub-1545\">[clatter of telephone buttons]</p><p begin=\"01:22:01.19\" end=\"01:22:01.97\" xml:id=\"sub-1546\">You callin' him?</p><p begin=\"01:22:03.08\" end=\"01:22:03.61\" xml:id=\"sub-1547\">Creegan.</p><p begin=\"01:22:15.70\" end=\"01:22:16.41\" xml:id=\"sub-1548\">[clunk of telephone handset]</p><p begin=\"01:22:17.19\" end=\"01:22:18.18\" xml:id=\"sub-1549\">You don't need 'im, Susan.</p><p begin=\"01:22:20.69\" end=\"01:22:21.39\" xml:id=\"sub-1550\">Just you and me.</p><p begin=\"01:22:24.58\" end=\"01:22:25.37\" xml:id=\"sub-1551\">- What are you doing?</p><p begin=\"01:22:27.01\" end=\"01:22:27.91\" xml:id=\"sub-1552\">- Giving you another chance...</p><p begin=\"01:22:28.01\" end=\"01:22:28.61\" xml:id=\"sub-1553\">[snap-snap-snap]</p><p begin=\"01:22:30.09\" end=\"01:22:31.54\" xml:id=\"sub-1554\">to make the right choice.</p><p begin=\"01:22:31.83\" end=\"01:22:32.58\" xml:id=\"sub-1555\">- Stop it.</p><p begin=\"01:22:34.18\" end=\"01:22:34.86\" xml:id=\"sub-1556\">- You and me.</p><p begin=\"01:22:36.11\" end=\"01:22:37.20\" xml:id=\"sub-1557\">We belong together.</p><p begin=\"01:22:37.60\" end=\"01:22:38.40\" xml:id=\"sub-1558\">Need each other.</p><p begin=\"01:22:40.28\" end=\"01:22:41.55\" xml:id=\"sub-1559\">I would do anything for you.</p><p begin=\"01:22:44.09\" end=\"01:22:45.14\" xml:id=\"sub-1560\">You just have to name it.</p><p begin=\"01:22:46.03\" end=\"01:22:46.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1561\">- Get dressed.</p><p begin=\"01:22:47.45\" end=\"01:22:48.80\" xml:id=\"sub-1562\">- Just think what we <br/>could be together.</p><p begin=\"01:22:55.92\" end=\"01:22:56.42\" xml:id=\"sub-1563\">[click-click]</p><p begin=\"01:22:56.50\" end=\"01:22:57.54\" xml:id=\"sub-1564\">[click-click-click]</p><p begin=\"01:22:57.69\" end=\"01:22:58.23\" xml:id=\"sub-1565\">[click-click]</p><p begin=\"01:22:58.60\" end=\"01:22:59.10\" xml:id=\"sub-1566\">[click]</p><p begin=\"01:22:59.24\" end=\"01:22:59.74\" xml:id=\"sub-1567\">[click]</p><p begin=\"01:22:59.86\" end=\"01:23:01.55\" xml:id=\"sub-1568\">I thought about trustin' <br/>you.  I really did.</p><p begin=\"01:23:03.96\" end=\"01:23:05.18\" xml:id=\"sub-1569\">A little voice said, &quot;No.&quot;</p><p begin=\"01:23:07.52\" end=\"01:23:08.41\" xml:id=\"sub-1570\">The voice was right.</p><p begin=\"01:23:09.15\" end=\"01:23:09.74\" xml:id=\"sub-1571\">[sniffle]</p><p begin=\"01:23:18.66\" end=\"01:23:19.84\" xml:id=\"sub-1572\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Creegan] Tomorrow's <br/>front page.</span></p><p begin=\"01:23:24.10\" end=\"01:23:27.17\" xml:id=\"sub-1573\">[police sirens wail]</p><p begin=\"01:23:31.80\" end=\"01:23:32.53\" xml:id=\"sub-1574\">[car doors slam]</p><p begin=\"01:23:36.10\" end=\"01:23:36.82\" xml:id=\"sub-1575\">[door clicks open]</p><p begin=\"01:23:37.04\" end=\"01:23:39.42\" xml:id=\"sub-1576\">♪ [suspenseful music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:23:49.83\" end=\"01:23:50.43\" xml:id=\"sub-1577\">[Creegan] Susan!</p><p begin=\"01:23:52.15\" end=\"01:23:53.34\" xml:id=\"sub-1578\">[wind whistling]</p><p begin=\"01:24:01.10\" end=\"01:24:02.42\" xml:id=\"sub-1579\">[clatter of typewriter]</p><p begin=\"01:24:03.10\" end=\"01:24:03.73\" xml:id=\"sub-1580\">[muffled breathing]</p><p begin=\"01:24:09.28\" end=\"01:24:10.14\" xml:id=\"sub-1581\">Welcome home.</p><p begin=\"01:24:12.98\" end=\"01:24:13.54\" xml:id=\"sub-1582\">- Why here?</p><p begin=\"01:24:17.97\" end=\"01:24:19.39\" xml:id=\"sub-1583\">- The scene of your great arrest</p><p begin=\"01:24:20.86\" end=\"01:24:22.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1584\">and Creegan's big mistake.</p><p begin=\"01:24:26.09\" end=\"01:24:27.56\" xml:id=\"sub-1585\">[Enwright] I've managed to <br/>swing some extra manpower.</p><p begin=\"01:24:27.68\" end=\"01:24:29.41\" xml:id=\"sub-1586\">We've got over 100 officers <br/>at our disposal.</p><p begin=\"01:24:29.57\" end=\"01:24:30.08\" xml:id=\"sub-1587\">- The question is,</p><p begin=\"01:24:30.13\" end=\"01:24:30.89\" xml:id=\"sub-1588\">Where do they start looking?</p><p begin=\"01:24:31.07\" end=\"01:24:31.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1589\">- [Rivers] He could be anywhere.</p><p begin=\"01:24:32.08\" end=\"01:24:34.38\" xml:id=\"sub-1590\">- [Marion] The fact that he sent a <br/>message suggests he's ego-driven.</p><p begin=\"01:24:34.79\" end=\"01:24:36.08\" xml:id=\"sub-1591\">He has a need <br/>to let us know...</p><p begin=\"01:24:36.22\" end=\"01:24:37.20\" xml:id=\"sub-1592\">to involve us.</p><p begin=\"01:24:37.40\" end=\"01:24:38.64\" xml:id=\"sub-1593\">It isn't enough for him to kill.</p><p begin=\"01:24:38.86\" end=\"01:24:41.17\" xml:id=\"sub-1594\">He has a desire to feel clever...<br/>to feel he's outsmarting us.</p><p begin=\"01:24:41.52\" end=\"01:24:42.67\" xml:id=\"sub-1595\">- [Enwright] Which means we <br/>might have missed something.</p><p begin=\"01:24:43.07\" end=\"01:24:44.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1596\">- Emerson knows where she is.</p><p begin=\"01:24:45.67\" end=\"01:24:46.23\" xml:id=\"sub-1597\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Laney] Who's this?</span></p><p begin=\"01:24:47.46\" end=\"01:24:48.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1598\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Taylor] Where <br/>did you get that?</span></p><p begin=\"01:24:48.51\" end=\"01:24:51.38\" xml:id=\"sub-1599\">- Bedroom chest, bottom <br/>drawer, under old tights.</p><p begin=\"01:24:52.14\" end=\"01:24:53.18\" xml:id=\"sub-1600\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">Someone special?</span></p><p begin=\"01:24:54.00\" end=\"01:24:55.38\" xml:id=\"sub-1601\">- His name's Jonathan.</p><p begin=\"01:24:55.81\" end=\"01:24:56.73\" xml:id=\"sub-1602\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">An old boyfriend?</span></p><p begin=\"01:24:56.87\" end=\"01:24:57.51\" xml:id=\"sub-1603\">- We were engaged.</p><p begin=\"01:24:57.63\" end=\"01:24:58.33\" xml:id=\"sub-1604\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">Where is he now?</span></p><p begin=\"01:24:59.72\" end=\"01:25:00.30\" xml:id=\"sub-1605\">- He died.</p><p begin=\"01:25:01.69\" end=\"01:25:02.34\" xml:id=\"sub-1606\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">Shame.</span></p><p begin=\"01:25:05.11\" end=\"01:25:06.87\" xml:id=\"sub-1607\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">And you've never found <br/>anyone like him since?</span></p><p begin=\"01:25:08.12\" end=\"01:25:10.40\" xml:id=\"sub-1608\">You keep looking, hoping <br/>this will be the one...</p><p begin=\"01:25:10.68\" end=\"01:25:11.59\" xml:id=\"sub-1609\">but it's never the same.</p><p begin=\"01:25:12.71\" end=\"01:25:13.70\" xml:id=\"sub-1610\">All those partners.</p><p begin=\"01:25:14.16\" end=\"01:25:15.17\" xml:id=\"sub-1611\">All those men.</p><p begin=\"01:25:15.91\" end=\"01:25:17.66\" xml:id=\"sub-1612\">None of them were ever Jonathan.</p><p begin=\"01:25:18.46\" end=\"01:25:19.54\" xml:id=\"sub-1613\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">Why you doing this?</span></p><p begin=\"01:25:21.46\" end=\"01:25:22.17\" xml:id=\"sub-1614\">- What about me?</p><p begin=\"01:25:23.01\" end=\"01:25:24.09\" xml:id=\"sub-1615\">How did I compare?</p><p begin=\"01:25:25.67\" end=\"01:25:26.17\" xml:id=\"sub-1616\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">You didn't.</span></p><p begin=\"01:25:27.14\" end=\"01:25:28.12\" xml:id=\"sub-1617\">- What about Creegan?</p><p begin=\"01:25:29.93\" end=\"01:25:30.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1618\">Nobody compares.</p><p begin=\"01:25:33.49\" end=\"01:25:34.57\" xml:id=\"sub-1619\">- You're lucky, you know that.</p><p begin=\"01:25:36.68\" end=\"01:25:37.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1620\">- Right now I don't <br/>feel so lucky.</p><p begin=\"01:25:38.78\" end=\"01:25:40.70\" xml:id=\"sub-1621\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">Well, you had someone special, <br/>even for just a short time.</span></p><p begin=\"01:25:40.82\" end=\"01:25:42.38\" xml:id=\"sub-1622\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">Some people go through <br/>their whole lives...</span></p><p begin=\"01:25:42.50\" end=\"01:25:43.41\" xml:id=\"sub-1623\">looking, hoping...</p><p begin=\"01:25:44.49\" end=\"01:25:45.36\" xml:id=\"sub-1624\">Nothing happens.</p><p begin=\"01:25:46.64\" end=\"01:25:47.28\" xml:id=\"sub-1625\">- Like you?</p><p begin=\"01:25:48.83\" end=\"01:25:49.92\" xml:id=\"sub-1626\">- I thought maybe <br/>you were special.</p><p begin=\"01:25:51.52\" end=\"01:25:52.57\" xml:id=\"sub-1627\">I didn't reckon on Creegan.</p><p begin=\"01:25:52.85\" end=\"01:25:53.40\" xml:id=\"sub-1628\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">I've told you before...</span></p><p begin=\"01:25:53.44\" end=\"01:25:53.94\" xml:id=\"sub-1629\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">There's nothing between--</span></p><p begin=\"01:25:54.04\" end=\"01:25:54.56\" xml:id=\"sub-1630\">- Don't lie to me.</p><p begin=\"01:25:54.66\" end=\"01:25:55.37\" xml:id=\"sub-1631\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Taylor] I'm not lying...</span></p><p begin=\"01:25:55.54\" end=\"01:25:56.27\" xml:id=\"sub-1632\">- YOU'RE ALWAYS LYING!</p><p begin=\"01:25:56.73\" end=\"01:25:57.37\" xml:id=\"sub-1633\">Cheating...</p><p begin=\"01:25:57.49\" end=\"01:25:58.59\" xml:id=\"sub-1634\">Anything to get where <br/>you want to go...</p><p begin=\"01:25:58.79\" end=\"01:26:00.46\" xml:id=\"sub-1635\">It doesn't matter how many <br/>people get screwed!</p><p begin=\"01:26:02.47\" end=\"01:26:03.36\" xml:id=\"sub-1636\">- [quietly] That's not true.</p><p begin=\"01:26:07.65\" end=\"01:26:08.61\" xml:id=\"sub-1637\">- You want me <br/>to tear this up?</p><p begin=\"01:26:09.82\" end=\"01:26:10.38\" xml:id=\"sub-1638\">- What does it matter?</p><p begin=\"01:26:10.49\" end=\"01:26:11.37\" xml:id=\"sub-1639\">You're gonna <br/>kill me anyway.</p><p begin=\"01:26:12.54\" end=\"01:26:14.49\" xml:id=\"sub-1640\">[cell doors click open]</p><p begin=\"01:26:15.34\" end=\"01:26:19.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1641\">[hollow footsteps]</p><p begin=\"01:26:20.12\" end=\"01:26:21.17\" xml:id=\"sub-1642\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Creegan] Laney <br/>kidnapped Taylor.</span></p><p begin=\"01:26:21.81\" end=\"01:26:22.76\" xml:id=\"sub-1643\">- I had a feeling he would.</p><p begin=\"01:26:22.98\" end=\"01:26:24.52\" xml:id=\"sub-1644\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Creegan] And do you have a feeling <br/>where he  might have taken her?</span></p><p begin=\"01:26:25.19\" end=\"01:26:26.38\" xml:id=\"sub-1645\">- I have some ideas.</p><p begin=\"01:26:26.74\" end=\"01:26:27.40\" xml:id=\"sub-1646\">- So tell us.</p><p begin=\"01:26:28.32\" end=\"01:26:30.41\" xml:id=\"sub-1647\">- Oh, events must take <br/>their natural course.</p><p begin=\"01:26:30.79\" end=\"01:26:32.16\" xml:id=\"sub-1648\">I can't interfere.</p><p begin=\"01:26:35.15\" end=\"01:26:36.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1649\">- What have you got to lose?</p><p begin=\"01:26:37.02\" end=\"01:26:38.35\" xml:id=\"sub-1650\">- My life's work.</p><p begin=\"01:26:40.50\" end=\"01:26:41.36\" xml:id=\"sub-1651\">I must prevail.</p><p begin=\"01:26:43.78\" end=\"01:26:45.21\" xml:id=\"sub-1652\">I think I've said enough.</p><p begin=\"01:26:50.11\" end=\"01:26:51.36\" xml:id=\"sub-1653\">- That night we were together...</p><p begin=\"01:26:55.07\" end=\"01:26:57.18\" xml:id=\"sub-1654\">I haven't felt so close to <br/>anyone in a long time.</p><p begin=\"01:27:00.11\" end=\"01:27:01.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1655\">I thought you should know.</p><p begin=\"01:27:04.17\" end=\"01:27:05.85\" xml:id=\"sub-1656\">- I wondered how long <br/>it would take you.</p><p begin=\"01:27:07.30\" end=\"01:27:07.80\" xml:id=\"sub-1657\">- What?</p><p begin=\"01:27:08.31\" end=\"01:27:09.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1658\">- Cheap psychology.</p><p begin=\"01:27:09.37\" end=\"01:27:10.75\" xml:id=\"sub-1659\">Get his trust.<br/>Keep him sweet.</p><p begin=\"01:27:11.15\" end=\"01:27:11.86\" xml:id=\"sub-1660\">- It's the truth.</p><p begin=\"01:27:12.14\" end=\"01:27:12.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1661\">- It's your job.</p><p begin=\"01:27:14.46\" end=\"01:27:16.63\" xml:id=\"sub-1662\">Right now, you'd say or <br/>do anything to survive.</p><p begin=\"01:27:17.44\" end=\"01:27:17.97\" xml:id=\"sub-1663\">- No.</p><p begin=\"01:27:18.15\" end=\"01:27:20.57\" xml:id=\"sub-1664\">- Oh, I love you, David. <br/>You're so great.</p><p begin=\"01:27:20.88\" end=\"01:27:21.90\" xml:id=\"sub-1665\">- I know what happens.</p><p begin=\"01:27:23.04\" end=\"01:27:24.19\" xml:id=\"sub-1666\">I've seen it before, remember?</p><p begin=\"01:27:26.08\" end=\"01:27:27.60\" xml:id=\"sub-1667\">- Emerson brought us here,</p><p begin=\"01:27:27.94\" end=\"01:27:30.32\" xml:id=\"sub-1668\">and Emerson will force you to kill me.</p><p begin=\"01:27:41.00\" end=\"01:27:41.54\" xml:id=\"sub-1669\">[thwack]</p><p begin=\"01:27:46.09\" end=\"01:27:46.70\" xml:id=\"sub-1670\">[THWACK]<br/>[groan of frustration]</p><p begin=\"01:27:49.01\" end=\"01:27:50.10\" xml:id=\"sub-1671\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Marion] No luck with Emerson?</span></p><p begin=\"01:27:50.62\" end=\"01:27:51.94\" xml:id=\"sub-1672\">- Ah-h, I can't find his weakness.</p><p begin=\"01:27:52.30\" end=\"01:27:53.14\" xml:id=\"sub-1673\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Marion] It'll be there.</span></p><p begin=\"01:27:54.05\" end=\"01:27:56.47\" xml:id=\"sub-1674\">- You said guilt would <br/>weaken his self-esteem.</p><p begin=\"01:27:56.64\" end=\"01:27:57.74\" xml:id=\"sub-1675\">Well, I've seen no sign of that.</p><p begin=\"01:27:59.05\" end=\"01:28:01.84\" xml:id=\"sub-1676\">I mean, this guy honestly believes <br/>he's gonna go on forever.</p><p begin=\"01:28:02.71\" end=\"01:28:04.58\" xml:id=\"sub-1677\">- But what would it take <br/>to maintain that belief?</p><p begin=\"01:28:08.32\" end=\"01:28:09.16\" xml:id=\"sub-1678\">- More killings.</p><p begin=\"01:28:09.56\" end=\"01:28:12.14\" xml:id=\"sub-1679\">- And, as he can't do them himself, <br/>he experiences them by proxy.</p><p begin=\"01:28:14.66\" end=\"01:28:15.90\" xml:id=\"sub-1680\">- Taylor giving him the lock of hair.</p><p begin=\"01:28:16.10\" end=\"01:28:16.86\" xml:id=\"sub-1681\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Marion] Exactly.</span></p><p begin=\"01:28:17.08\" end=\"01:28:18.68\" xml:id=\"sub-1682\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">He believes he's continuing <br/>through others,</span></p><p begin=\"01:28:18.79\" end=\"01:28:20.41\" xml:id=\"sub-1683\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">and, in a strange way,<br/>he's right.</span></p><p begin=\"01:28:22.61\" end=\"01:28:23.56\" xml:id=\"sub-1684\">- Wait a minute.</p><p begin=\"01:28:25.55\" end=\"01:28:26.05\" xml:id=\"sub-1685\">- What?</p><p begin=\"01:28:27.68\" end=\"01:28:28.38\" xml:id=\"sub-1686\">- His weakness.</p><p begin=\"01:28:31.11\" end=\"01:28:32.43\" xml:id=\"sub-1687\">He needs people to believe in 'im.</p><p begin=\"01:28:32.67\" end=\"01:28:33.28\" xml:id=\"sub-1688\">­♪ [music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:28:33.45\" end=\"01:28:34.04\" xml:id=\"sub-1689\">[computer beep]</p><p begin=\"01:28:34.15\" end=\"01:28:34.71\" xml:id=\"sub-1690\">­♪ [music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:28:36.17\" end=\"01:28:36.67\" xml:id=\"sub-1691\">[computer beep]</p><p begin=\"01:28:36.81\" end=\"01:28:37.40\" xml:id=\"sub-1692\">­♪ [music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:28:42.73\" end=\"01:28:43.29\" xml:id=\"sub-1693\">[keyboard click-click-click]</p><p begin=\"01:28:43.40\" end=\"01:28:43.90\" xml:id=\"sub-1694\">[computer beep]</p><p begin=\"01:28:44.05\" end=\"01:28:44.59\" xml:id=\"sub-1695\">­♪ [music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:28:45.30\" end=\"01:28:45.91\" xml:id=\"sub-1696\">[computer beep]</p><p begin=\"01:28:46.05\" end=\"01:28:46.60\" xml:id=\"sub-1697\">­♪ [music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:28:48.87\" end=\"01:28:49.42\" xml:id=\"sub-1698\">[computer beep]</p><p begin=\"01:28:49.52\" end=\"01:28:50.14\" xml:id=\"sub-1699\">­♪ [music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:28:54.02\" end=\"01:28:54.66\" xml:id=\"sub-1700\">[computer beep]</p><p begin=\"01:28:54.83\" end=\"01:28:55.47\" xml:id=\"sub-1701\">­♪ [music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:28:57.16\" end=\"01:28:57.66\" xml:id=\"sub-1702\">[computer beep]</p><p begin=\"01:28:58.10\" end=\"01:28:59.38\" xml:id=\"sub-1703\">­♪ [music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:29:08.38\" end=\"01:29:09.11\" xml:id=\"sub-1704\">[computer beep]</p><p begin=\"01:29:09.27\" end=\"01:29:10.11\" xml:id=\"sub-1705\">­♪ [music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:29:12.23\" end=\"01:29:12.84\" xml:id=\"sub-1706\">[computer beep]</p><p begin=\"01:29:13.06\" end=\"01:29:13.70\" xml:id=\"sub-1707\">- That's perfect.</p><p begin=\"01:29:14.73\" end=\"01:29:15.29\" xml:id=\"sub-1708\">Thanks.</p><p begin=\"01:29:15.42\" end=\"01:29:17.57\" xml:id=\"sub-1709\">­♪ [music ends abruptly] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:29:18.36\" end=\"01:29:19.21\" xml:id=\"sub-1710\">Tell me about Laney.</p><p begin=\"01:29:19.69\" end=\"01:29:20.68\" xml:id=\"sub-1711\">- Your relationship with 'im.</p><p begin=\"01:29:21.08\" end=\"01:29:22.18\" xml:id=\"sub-1712\">- Our relationship?</p><p begin=\"01:29:22.89\" end=\"01:29:23.69\" xml:id=\"sub-1713\">Teacher, pupil.</p><p begin=\"01:29:23.92\" end=\"01:29:24.62\" xml:id=\"sub-1714\">Master, student.</p><p begin=\"01:29:25.12\" end=\"01:29:27.11\" xml:id=\"sub-1715\">Oh, he was so repressed.<br/>I set him free.</p><p begin=\"01:29:27.38\" end=\"01:29:28.93\" xml:id=\"sub-1716\">- And now you live <br/>on through him.</p><p begin=\"01:29:29.33\" end=\"01:29:30.39\" xml:id=\"sub-1717\">- Oh, the power lives on.</p><p begin=\"01:29:30.68\" end=\"01:29:31.55\" xml:id=\"sub-1718\">We simply serve it.</p><p begin=\"01:29:32.14\" end=\"01:29:33.51\" xml:id=\"sub-1719\">- He made you into <br/>a household name.</p><p begin=\"01:29:34.20\" end=\"01:29:35.45\" xml:id=\"sub-1720\">- He simply wrote what he saw.</p><p begin=\"01:29:36.43\" end=\"01:29:38.11\" xml:id=\"sub-1721\">- He got you your place <br/>in the history books.</p><p begin=\"01:29:39.94\" end=\"01:29:40.70\" xml:id=\"sub-1722\">- Where is this leading us?</p><p begin=\"01:29:41.08\" end=\"01:29:42.39\" xml:id=\"sub-1723\">- To today's paper...</p><p begin=\"01:29:44.77\" end=\"01:29:46.74\" xml:id=\"sub-1724\">[rustle of newspaper]</p><p begin=\"01:29:55.65\" end=\"01:29:57.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1725\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Creegan] He's taken <br/>over, Emerson.</span></p><p begin=\"01:29:59.15\" end=\"01:30:00.42\" xml:id=\"sub-1726\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">Donning your mantle.</span></p><p begin=\"01:30:02.59\" end=\"01:30:03.39\" xml:id=\"sub-1727\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Emerson] He wouldn't.</span></p><p begin=\"01:30:04.08\" end=\"01:30:05.67\" xml:id=\"sub-1728\">- He's taking the credit for <br/>all the other murders.</p><p begin=\"01:30:09.78\" end=\"01:30:10.85\" xml:id=\"sub-1729\">- You know that's not true.</p><p begin=\"01:30:11.15\" end=\"01:30:12.17\" xml:id=\"sub-1730\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Creegan] Oh, I know.</span></p><p begin=\"01:30:15.12\" end=\"01:30:16.34\" xml:id=\"sub-1731\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">But what will the public think?</span></p><p begin=\"01:30:17.83\" end=\"01:30:19.17\" xml:id=\"sub-1732\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">What will the history books say?</span></p><p begin=\"01:30:22.70\" end=\"01:30:23.50\" xml:id=\"sub-1733\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Taylor] What are you waiting for?</span></p><p begin=\"01:30:25.32\" end=\"01:30:26.19\" xml:id=\"sub-1734\">Why don't you kill me now?</p><p begin=\"01:30:27.00\" end=\"01:30:28.80\" xml:id=\"sub-1735\">- Everything at the <br/>appropriate time.</p><p begin=\"01:30:29.41\" end=\"01:30:30.67\" xml:id=\"sub-1736\">- You're waiting for <br/>Creegan to find me.</p><p begin=\"01:30:32.86\" end=\"01:30:33.44\" xml:id=\"sub-1737\">What if he doesn't?</p><p begin=\"01:30:33.95\" end=\"01:30:34.45\" xml:id=\"sub-1738\">- He will.</p><p begin=\"01:30:36.36\" end=\"01:30:39.13\" xml:id=\"sub-1739\">- When you kill me, what <br/>will be the reason?</p><p begin=\"01:30:39.55\" end=\"01:30:40.06\" xml:id=\"sub-1740\">- Reason?</p><p begin=\"01:30:40.78\" end=\"01:30:41.44\" xml:id=\"sub-1741\">I don't need a reason.</p><p begin=\"01:30:42.53\" end=\"01:30:45.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1742\">I just have to be myself.<br/>My natural self.</p><p begin=\"01:30:45.35\" end=\"01:30:46.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1743\">- You're even beginning <br/>to sound like Emerson.</p><p begin=\"01:30:48.51\" end=\"01:30:49.85\" xml:id=\"sub-1744\">I don't believe you want <br/>to be doing this...</p><p begin=\"01:30:50.92\" end=\"01:30:51.75\" xml:id=\"sub-1745\">not the real you.</p><p begin=\"01:30:54.04\" end=\"01:30:55.39\" xml:id=\"sub-1746\">- What would you know <br/>about the real me?</p><p begin=\"01:30:56.61\" end=\"01:30:58.20\" xml:id=\"sub-1747\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">I know the &quot;you&quot;<br/>I saw that night.</span></p><p begin=\"01:31:00.12\" end=\"01:31:01.59\" xml:id=\"sub-1748\">- You thought you could <br/>manipulate 'im,</p><p begin=\"01:31:02.13\" end=\"01:31:02.65\" xml:id=\"sub-1749\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">control 'im...</span></p><p begin=\"01:31:02.83\" end=\"01:31:04.16\" xml:id=\"sub-1750\">- He's left you behind, Emerson.</p><p begin=\"01:31:04.33\" end=\"01:31:05.10\" xml:id=\"sub-1751\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Creegan]...stolen your image.</span></p><p begin=\"01:31:05.20\" end=\"01:31:06.17\" xml:id=\"sub-1752\">- Destroyed your reputation.</p><p begin=\"01:31:06.34\" end=\"01:31:07.38\" xml:id=\"sub-1753\">- Enough.</p><p begin=\"01:31:07.75\" end=\"01:31:09.55\" xml:id=\"sub-1754\">This is as it should be.</p><p begin=\"01:31:09.80\" end=\"01:31:11.39\" xml:id=\"sub-1755\">- He was the one<br/> manipulating you.</p><p begin=\"01:31:11.64\" end=\"01:31:12.23\" xml:id=\"sub-1756\">- No-o-o.</p><p begin=\"01:31:12.40\" end=\"01:31:13.69\" xml:id=\"sub-1757\">We had an agreement.</p><p begin=\"01:31:14.03\" end=\"01:31:17.65\" xml:id=\"sub-1758\">If ever I was killed or arrested, <br/>he would continue my work.</p><p begin=\"01:31:17.91\" end=\"01:31:18.64\" xml:id=\"sub-1759\">- It's his work now.</p><p begin=\"01:31:18.81\" end=\"01:31:19.36\" xml:id=\"sub-1760\">- No-o-o.</p><p begin=\"01:31:19.48\" end=\"01:31:20.39\" xml:id=\"sub-1761\">- [Rivers] He told you about Foulds.</p><p begin=\"01:31:20.65\" end=\"01:31:21.26\" xml:id=\"sub-1762\">- He...</p><p begin=\"01:31:21.80\" end=\"01:31:22.45\" xml:id=\"sub-1763\">This is...</p><p begin=\"01:31:22.95\" end=\"01:31:23.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1764\">This is wrong.</p><p begin=\"01:31:24.03\" end=\"01:31:25.10\" xml:id=\"sub-1765\">- You're losing control, Emerson.</p><p begin=\"01:31:25.27\" end=\"01:31:26.22\" xml:id=\"sub-1766\">- Laney has the control.</p><p begin=\"01:31:26.34\" end=\"01:31:27.74\" xml:id=\"sub-1767\">- I have the control.</p><p begin=\"01:31:27.88\" end=\"01:31:28.38\" xml:id=\"sub-1768\">Me!</p><p begin=\"01:31:28.48\" end=\"01:31:29.11\" xml:id=\"sub-1769\">ME!</p><p begin=\"01:31:32.02\" end=\"01:31:32.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1770\">- So use it.</p><p begin=\"01:31:41.28\" end=\"01:31:43.72\" xml:id=\"sub-1771\">- He told me about driving <br/>the woman to suicide.</p><p begin=\"01:31:44.79\" end=\"01:31:46.55\" xml:id=\"sub-1772\">He said he would do <br/>the same to Foulds.</p><p begin=\"01:31:46.69\" end=\"01:31:48.60\" xml:id=\"sub-1773\">I told him that wasn't enough.</p><p begin=\"01:31:49.08\" end=\"01:31:50.34\" xml:id=\"sub-1774\">Killing by proxy.</p><p begin=\"01:31:51.37\" end=\"01:31:53.56\" xml:id=\"sub-1775\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">You can't taste words.</span></p><p begin=\"01:31:53.82\" end=\"01:31:54.73\" xml:id=\"sub-1776\">- Where's Taylor?</p><p begin=\"01:31:55.34\" end=\"01:31:56.45\" xml:id=\"sub-1777\">- [Emerson] Did he leave <br/>a message?</p><p begin=\"01:31:56.83\" end=\"01:31:58.81\" xml:id=\"sub-1778\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Creegan] He said I'm <br/>sending you a reward.</span></p><p begin=\"01:32:01.00\" end=\"01:32:04.20\" xml:id=\"sub-1779\">- It's the same message I sent him <br/>before I killed Emily Hawkins.</p><p begin=\"01:32:07.09\" end=\"01:32:09.14\" xml:id=\"sub-1780\">- He's recreating her death.</p><p begin=\"01:32:11.66\" end=\"01:32:12.41\" xml:id=\"sub-1781\">- The shack.</p><p begin=\"01:32:13.14\" end=\"01:32:13.94\" xml:id=\"sub-1782\">[hurried footsteps]</p><p begin=\"01:32:14.09\" end=\"01:32:14.66\" xml:id=\"sub-1783\">- Creegan!</p><p begin=\"01:32:17.11\" end=\"01:32:18.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1784\">Don't hesitate this time.</p><p begin=\"01:32:24.08\" end=\"01:32:27.13\" xml:id=\"sub-1785\">[hurried footsteps fade]</p><p begin=\"01:32:30.64\" end=\"01:32:31.90\" xml:id=\"sub-1786\">- You think you know the real me?</p><p begin=\"01:32:34.33\" end=\"01:32:35.19\" xml:id=\"sub-1787\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">Do you know this man?</span></p><p begin=\"01:32:36.58\" end=\"01:32:37.08\" xml:id=\"sub-1788\">[click of recording device]</p><p begin=\"01:32:39.08\" end=\"01:32:40.13\" xml:id=\"sub-1789\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[recording of Laney's voice] Sometimes <br/>I have this daydream.</span></p><p begin=\"01:32:41.01\" end=\"01:32:43.37\" xml:id=\"sub-1790\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">It can happen at any time. I can <br/>be walkin' down some street.</span></p><p begin=\"01:32:44.14\" end=\"01:32:45.10\" xml:id=\"sub-1791\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[recording of Emerson's voice] <br/>Whaddya see?</span></p><p begin=\"01:32:46.34\" end=\"01:32:49.18\" xml:id=\"sub-1792\">- [Laney's voice] Women. Strangers.  <br/>I don't know them, but I watch them.</p><p begin=\"01:32:49.77\" end=\"01:32:51.43\" xml:id=\"sub-1793\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Emerson's voice] Do they <br/>know they're being watched?</span></p><p begin=\"01:32:51.63\" end=\"01:32:52.52\" xml:id=\"sub-1794\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Laney's voice] Sometimes.</span></p><p begin=\"01:32:52.67\" end=\"01:32:53.73\" xml:id=\"sub-1795\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Emerson's voice] And <br/>how do they react?</span></p><p begin=\"01:32:54.16\" end=\"01:32:54.81\" xml:id=\"sub-1796\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Laney's voice] Fear.</span></p><p begin=\"01:32:55.87\" end=\"01:32:58.24\" xml:id=\"sub-1797\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">They catch me watching. <br/>I see fear in their eyes.</span></p><p begin=\"01:32:59.42\" end=\"01:33:00.70\" xml:id=\"sub-1798\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Emerson's voice] How <br/>does that make you feel?</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:01.84\" end=\"01:33:02.46\" xml:id=\"sub-1799\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Laney's voice] In control.</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:03.65\" end=\"01:33:04.57\" xml:id=\"sub-1800\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">And then the daydream comes, </span></p><p begin=\"01:33:04.68\" end=\"01:33:07.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1801\">and it seems as if I'm following <br/>someone, hunting them down.</p><p begin=\"01:33:07.51\" end=\"01:33:08.38\" xml:id=\"sub-1802\">- [Emerson's voice] Do you kill them...</p><p begin=\"01:33:09.10\" end=\"01:33:09.94\" xml:id=\"sub-1803\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">in your dream?</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:11.45\" end=\"01:33:12.09\" xml:id=\"sub-1804\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Laney's voice] Not to begin with...</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:12.20\" end=\"01:33:13.13\" xml:id=\"sub-1805\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">but lately...</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:13.79\" end=\"01:33:14.57\" xml:id=\"sub-1806\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">I'm not sure.</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:15.85\" end=\"01:33:18.24\" xml:id=\"sub-1807\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Emerson's voice] How do you feel <br/>if I told you these are not dreams?</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:19.24\" end=\"01:33:20.16\" xml:id=\"sub-1808\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Laney's voice] Of course <br/>they're dreams.</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:20.39\" end=\"01:33:22.18\" xml:id=\"sub-1809\">- [Emerson's voice] What are <br/>dreams but alternate realities?</p><p begin=\"01:33:22.52\" end=\"01:33:24.86\" xml:id=\"sub-1810\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">A parallel dominion where <br/>you can be king.</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:27.53\" end=\"01:33:28.90\" xml:id=\"sub-1811\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Laney's voice] I haven't <br/>actually killed  anyone.</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:29.15\" end=\"01:33:29.97\" xml:id=\"sub-1812\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Emerson's voice] How <br/>can you know?</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:30.50\" end=\"01:33:32.58\" xml:id=\"sub-1813\"><span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">What's imagined...what's real...</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:34.52\" end=\"01:33:36.24\" xml:id=\"sub-1814\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Laney's voice] What are you saying? <br/>That I've killed these women?</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:37.05\" end=\"01:33:38.25\" xml:id=\"sub-1815\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Emerson's voice] How <br/>would you feel if you had?</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:40.05\" end=\"01:33:40.73\" xml:id=\"sub-1816\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Laney's voice] Complete.</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:41.60\" end=\"01:33:42.13\" xml:id=\"sub-1817\">[recording device clicks off]</p><p begin=\"01:33:45.65\" end=\"01:33:46.60\" xml:id=\"sub-1818\">- The real me.</p><p begin=\"01:33:48.49\" end=\"01:33:49.75\" xml:id=\"sub-1819\">- Do you think this <br/>is a dream, David?</p><p begin=\"01:33:50.40\" end=\"01:33:50.90\" xml:id=\"sub-1820\">- <span tts:fontStyle=\"italic\">[Laney] What?</span></p><p begin=\"01:33:51.67\" end=\"01:33:52.26\" xml:id=\"sub-1821\">- All of this?</p><p begin=\"01:33:52.33\" end=\"01:33:52.83\" xml:id=\"sub-1822\">Us?</p><p begin=\"01:33:53.32\" end=\"01:33:54.19\" xml:id=\"sub-1823\">It's just a dream to you?</p><p begin=\"01:33:55.00\" end=\"01:33:57.19\" xml:id=\"sub-1824\">- Nobody knows for sure what's <br/>real and what's imagined.</p><p begin=\"01:33:57.42\" end=\"01:33:58.37\" xml:id=\"sub-1825\">- This is real, David.</p><p begin=\"01:34:00.13\" end=\"01:34:00.84\" xml:id=\"sub-1826\">These ropes are real.</p><p begin=\"01:34:01.22\" end=\"01:34:02.48\" xml:id=\"sub-1827\">That knife's real. <br/>You and me.</p><p begin=\"01:34:03.01\" end=\"01:34:03.52\" xml:id=\"sub-1828\">- Shut up.</p><p begin=\"01:34:04.12\" end=\"01:34:06.19\" xml:id=\"sub-1829\">- Emerson was manipulating you,</p><p begin=\"01:34:06.54\" end=\"01:34:07.30\" xml:id=\"sub-1830\">and he still is.</p><p begin=\"01:34:07.38\" end=\"01:34:07.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1831\">- No.</p><p begin=\"01:34:08.62\" end=\"01:34:09.18\" xml:id=\"sub-1832\">My choice.</p><p begin=\"01:34:10.27\" end=\"01:34:11.20\" xml:id=\"sub-1833\">I let him inside.</p><p begin=\"01:34:12.80\" end=\"01:34:15.20\" xml:id=\"sub-1834\">[racing car engine]</p><p begin=\"01:34:15.42\" end=\"01:34:16.19\" xml:id=\"sub-1835\">- I should go in.</p><p begin=\"01:34:17.67\" end=\"01:34:19.85\" xml:id=\"sub-1836\">If he's recreating Emily's death, <br/>he needs you to be there.</p><p begin=\"01:34:20.41\" end=\"01:34:21.56\" xml:id=\"sub-1837\">Maybe he won't kill her if it's me.</p><p begin=\"01:34:21.88\" end=\"01:34:22.55\" xml:id=\"sub-1838\">- I have to go in.</p><p begin=\"01:34:24.15\" end=\"01:34:24.92\" xml:id=\"sub-1839\">- You don't have to worry.</p><p begin=\"01:34:25.00\" end=\"01:34:25.50\" xml:id=\"sub-1840\">I can do this.</p><p begin=\"01:34:25.65\" end=\"01:34:26.21\" xml:id=\"sub-1841\">- Another time.</p><p begin=\"01:34:28.10\" end=\"01:34:29.10\" xml:id=\"sub-1842\">Laney's mine.</p><p begin=\"01:34:31.87\" end=\"01:34:35.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1843\">[car engine racing]</p><p begin=\"01:34:36.79\" end=\"01:34:37.95\" xml:id=\"sub-1844\">The first time I killed a man,</p><p begin=\"01:34:39.38\" end=\"01:34:40.43\" xml:id=\"sub-1845\">it nearly destroyed me.</p><p begin=\"01:34:43.10\" end=\"01:34:43.60\" xml:id=\"sub-1846\">Me or him?</p><p begin=\"01:34:45.45\" end=\"01:34:46.21\" xml:id=\"sub-1847\">I had no choice.</p><p begin=\"01:34:49.36\" end=\"01:34:51.14\" xml:id=\"sub-1848\">I remember every detail.</p><p begin=\"01:34:53.22\" end=\"01:34:55.42\" xml:id=\"sub-1849\">Movement of every muscle <br/>on his face as he died.</p><p begin=\"01:34:58.50\" end=\"01:34:59.19\" xml:id=\"sub-1850\">I felt this...</p><p begin=\"01:35:01.24\" end=\"01:35:01.75\" xml:id=\"sub-1851\">rush...</p><p begin=\"01:35:02.94\" end=\"01:35:03.51\" xml:id=\"sub-1852\">of life.</p><p begin=\"01:35:05.55\" end=\"01:35:06.73\" xml:id=\"sub-1853\">The most alive I've ever felt.</p><p begin=\"01:35:08.21\" end=\"01:35:08.75\" xml:id=\"sub-1854\">- You enjoyed it.</p><p begin=\"01:35:10.35\" end=\"01:35:10.85\" xml:id=\"sub-1855\">- No,</p><p begin=\"01:35:13.37\" end=\"01:35:14.43\" xml:id=\"sub-1856\">but I didn't feel guilty,</p><p begin=\"01:35:16.73\" end=\"01:35:17.32\" xml:id=\"sub-1857\">not then.</p><p begin=\"01:35:18.34\" end=\"01:35:19.18\" xml:id=\"sub-1858\">No emotion.</p><p begin=\"01:35:19.89\" end=\"01:35:20.47\" xml:id=\"sub-1859\">But later,</p><p begin=\"01:35:22.65\" end=\"01:35:26.20\" xml:id=\"sub-1860\">when I had to watch him <br/>die over and over...</p><p begin=\"01:35:27.11\" end=\"01:35:28.16\" xml:id=\"sub-1861\">then there was emotion.</p><p begin=\"01:35:30.11\" end=\"01:35:30.88\" xml:id=\"sub-1862\">Too much.</p><p begin=\"01:35:32.85\" end=\"01:35:33.67\" xml:id=\"sub-1863\">- You felt that?</p><p begin=\"01:35:34.85\" end=\"01:35:35.48\" xml:id=\"sub-1864\">- I still do.</p><p begin=\"01:35:36.03\" end=\"01:35:36.79\" xml:id=\"sub-1865\">- How do you get it out?</p><p begin=\"01:35:37.62\" end=\"01:35:38.23\" xml:id=\"sub-1866\">Get rid of it?</p><p begin=\"01:35:38.78\" end=\"01:35:39.44\" xml:id=\"sub-1867\">- You don't.</p><p begin=\"01:35:41.35\" end=\"01:35:42.33\" xml:id=\"sub-1868\">While I'm still here,</p><p begin=\"01:35:44.15\" end=\"01:35:45.45\" xml:id=\"sub-1869\">there is hope, David.</p><p begin=\"01:35:47.81\" end=\"01:35:49.24\" xml:id=\"sub-1870\">I can help you find it.</p><p begin=\"01:35:50.23\" end=\"01:35:50.99\" xml:id=\"sub-1871\">- You'd help me?</p><p begin=\"01:35:53.07\" end=\"01:35:54.28\" xml:id=\"sub-1872\">- We can help each other.</p><p begin=\"01:35:58.79\" end=\"01:36:00.04\" xml:id=\"sub-1873\">- You really are special.</p><p begin=\"01:36:04.77\" end=\"01:36:07.20\" xml:id=\"sub-1874\">[rustle of undergrowth]</p><p begin=\"01:36:12.45\" end=\"01:36:12.96\" xml:id=\"sub-1875\">- You okay?</p><p begin=\"01:36:15.79\" end=\"01:36:16.40\" xml:id=\"sub-1876\">- Let's move it.</p><p begin=\"01:36:16.62\" end=\"01:36:17.23\" xml:id=\"sub-1877\">- So what do we do?</p><p begin=\"01:36:17.64\" end=\"01:36:18.35\" xml:id=\"sub-1878\">- You cover the front.</p><p begin=\"01:36:20.04\" end=\"01:36:22.70\" xml:id=\"sub-1879\">[hasty footsteps]</p><p begin=\"01:36:22.81\" end=\"01:36:25.54\" xml:id=\"sub-1880\">♪ [suspenseful music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:36:38.14\" end=\"01:36:38.74\" xml:id=\"sub-1881\">What's wrong?</p><p begin=\"01:36:41.02\" end=\"01:36:41.57\" xml:id=\"sub-1882\">Shit.</p><p begin=\"01:36:42.31\" end=\"01:36:42.96\" xml:id=\"sub-1883\">- David, no!</p><p begin=\"01:36:43.25\" end=\"01:36:44.25\" xml:id=\"sub-1884\">Y-y-you don't wanna do this.</p><p begin=\"01:36:44.45\" end=\"01:36:45.17\" xml:id=\"sub-1885\">- Shut up!<br/>[click]</p><p begin=\"01:36:45.43\" end=\"01:36:46.32\" xml:id=\"sub-1886\">- Don't kill 'im.</p><p begin=\"01:36:47.10\" end=\"01:36:48.19\" xml:id=\"sub-1887\">He won't kill me.</p><p begin=\"01:36:49.14\" end=\"01:36:49.86\" xml:id=\"sub-1888\">He won't.</p><p begin=\"01:36:51.17\" end=\"01:36:52.70\" xml:id=\"sub-1889\">He doesn't want to kill me.</p><p begin=\"01:36:52.86\" end=\"01:36:53.39\" xml:id=\"sub-1890\">- Shut up!</p><p begin=\"01:36:54.08\" end=\"01:36:55.41\" xml:id=\"sub-1891\">- Put the knife down, David.</p><p begin=\"01:36:56.15\" end=\"01:36:56.67\" xml:id=\"sub-1892\">- I can't.</p><p begin=\"01:36:59.21\" end=\"01:36:59.80\" xml:id=\"sub-1893\">I've been waitin'...</p><p begin=\"01:37:01.13\" end=\"01:37:01.83\" xml:id=\"sub-1894\">I have to...</p><p begin=\"01:37:02.04\" end=\"01:37:02.70\" xml:id=\"sub-1895\">I have to...</p><p begin=\"01:37:03.09\" end=\"01:37:05.19\" xml:id=\"sub-1896\">- He's not Emerson, Creegan.</p><p begin=\"01:37:06.70\" end=\"01:37:07.21\" xml:id=\"sub-1897\">- What?</p><p begin=\"01:37:07.55\" end=\"01:37:09.12\" xml:id=\"sub-1898\">- He isn't Emerson.</p><p begin=\"01:37:11.19\" end=\"01:37:13.41\" xml:id=\"sub-1899\">He doesn't want to kill <br/>me, and he won't.</p><p begin=\"01:37:15.08\" end=\"01:37:16.80\" xml:id=\"sub-1900\">Put the knife down, David.</p><p begin=\"01:37:17.78\" end=\"01:37:19.63\" xml:id=\"sub-1901\">You don't have to do anything <br/>you don't wanna do.</p><p begin=\"01:37:20.34\" end=\"01:37:22.15\" xml:id=\"sub-1902\">Put the knife down, <br/>and I'll help you.</p><p begin=\"01:37:30.87\" end=\"01:37:31.46\" xml:id=\"sub-1903\">[gunshot]</p><p begin=\"01:37:31.65\" end=\"01:37:32.20\" xml:id=\"sub-1904\">[Taylor gasps]</p><p begin=\"01:37:32.40\" end=\"01:37:33.18\" xml:id=\"sub-1905\">[thud]</p><p begin=\"01:37:34.82\" end=\"01:37:37.68\" xml:id=\"sub-1906\">♪ [dramatic music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:37:37.85\" end=\"01:37:40.32\" xml:id=\"sub-1907\">[heavy breathing]</p><p begin=\"01:37:40.79\" end=\"01:37:45.25\" xml:id=\"sub-1908\">♪ [dramatic music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:37:51.53\" end=\"01:37:52.71\" xml:id=\"sub-1909\">- [Creegan] Put the gun down, Mark.</p><p begin=\"01:37:53.34\" end=\"01:37:54.96\" xml:id=\"sub-1910\">[heavy breathing]</p><p begin=\"01:37:55.13\" end=\"01:37:56.41\" xml:id=\"sub-1911\">MARK, PUT THE GUN AWAY!</p><p begin=\"01:38:00.53\" end=\"01:38:02.58\" xml:id=\"sub-1912\">- You stupid bastard...</p><p begin=\"01:38:03.64\" end=\"01:38:04.14\" xml:id=\"sub-1913\">- What?</p><p begin=\"01:38:04.35\" end=\"01:38:06.21\" xml:id=\"sub-1914\">- He wasn't going to kill me.</p><p begin=\"01:38:06.32\" end=\"01:38:08.36\" xml:id=\"sub-1915\">- He had a bloody knife <br/>at your throat.</p><p begin=\"01:38:09.85\" end=\"01:38:11.34\" xml:id=\"sub-1916\">You saw it.  <br/>He had a knife...</p><p begin=\"01:38:17.12\" end=\"01:38:21.10\" xml:id=\"sub-1917\">­♪ [music] ♪</p><p begin=\"01:38:36.12\" end=\"01:38:44.17\" xml:id=\"sub-1918\">♪ [Touching <span tts:fontWeight=\"bold\">Evil</span> closing theme music] ♪</p></div> </body> </tt>";
